Text:
Hi,

@Zombie_Boy, from here (http://www.videohelp.com/tools/AVIAddXSubs ) I see that AVIAddXSubs works with mp4 if subtitles are in idx/sub format, so you just have to convert the srt provide with the movie with SubtitleCreator (http://www.videohelp.com/tools/SubtitleCreator ) to the idx/sub format.
@+
